# Commands

### Initialize project

``` terraform init ```

### Validate sintax

``` terraform validate ```

### View plan	 

``` terraform plan ```

### Deploy

``` terraform apply ```

### Delete deploy

``` terraform destroy ```

## View Deployment

`` terraform show ```

